      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SIOUX WARRIOR (4) drew wide and was held up for a luckless fourth when resuming then drew on the back line and raced wide in the latter stages as runner-up at Kilmore last week. Gets his best draw of the campaign so far and should be close to his peak third up. STEADY DREAM (2) comes off a strong showing for second here last time out. All three career wins have come at this distance and she is well served by another good draw. MISTA WALKER (8) put three wins together before missing by a head at Cranbourne last time out. Chased strongly along the sprint lane last start and could do the same from this draw. SPIRITED LASS (9) drew wide and worked last start so prepared to forgive that result and assess her chances off the resuming win from this row at Cranbourne prior.",
